# Majestic Events & Protocols Web Platform 👑
- live deom: [https://majestic-event-protocols.vercel.app/](https://majestic-event-protocols.vercel.app/) **Motto:** Poised, Prepared, and Purpose Driven.

This is the official digital home for **Majestic Events & Protocols**, a premier event planning agency specializing in high-end coordination, professional ushering, and ceremonial hosting.

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** Next.js / React.js
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS (Custom Gold/Brown Theme)
- **Animations:** Framer Motion (for "Majestic" transitions)
- **Icons:** Lucide React / FontAwesome
- **Deployment:** Vercel

## ✨ Key Features
- **Heroic Landing:** High-impact visual storytelling of luxury events.
- **Service Portfolio:** Detailed breakdown of planning, ushering, and MC services.
- **Dynamic Gallery:** Optimized image masonry for event showcases.
- **Lead Generation:** Integrated contact forms and floating WhatsApp communication.
- **Fully Responsive:** Seamless experience from mobile to 4K displays.

## 🎨 Design System
- **Primary:** `#A68946` (Majestic Brown)
- **Secondary:** `#FFFFFF` (Pure White)
- **Accent:** `#000000` (Royal Black)

